Finished the wig for my Io cosplay! I know in the reference it seems to have a darker color but in game her hair is whiter-light grey ~
Btw the base is a light grey wig with the ears sewn on it. The braids are made with foam rubber 💙

All my updates of my Io cosplay from Paladins!!
Swipe to see all the photos (and a stupid video where I smile, which is strange because I never smile in videos/photos 🙃)
I created the first braid (it is made of foam rubber, just have to create the other one), the ears, the dress (it's a wip),the bracers and some pieces that will be attached to the dress. I can't wait to finish this cosplay ✨🌙💙
